NY.GDP.COAL.RT.ZS-gg.def: Coal rents are the difference between the value of both hard and soft coal production at world prices and their total costs of production.
NY.GDP.COAL.RT.ZS-gg.name: Coal rents
NY.GDP.COAL.RT.ZS-gg.source: World Bank staff estimates based on sources and methods described in the World Bank's The Changing Wealth of Nations.

NY.GDP.FRST.RT.ZS-gg.def: Forest rents are roundwood harvest times the product of regional prices and a regional rental rate.
NY.GDP.FRST.RT.ZS-gg.name: Forest rents
NY.GDP.FRST.RT.ZS-gg.source: World Bank staff estimates based on sources and methods described in the World Bank's The Changing Wealth of Nations.

NY.GDP.MINR.RT.ZS-gg.def: Mineral rents are the difference between the value of production for a stock of minerals at world prices and their total costs of production. Minerals included in the calculation are tin, gold, lead, zinc, iron, copper, nickel, silver, bauxite, and phosphate.
NY.GDP.MINR.RT.ZS-gg.name: Mineral rents
NY.GDP.MINR.RT.ZS-gg.source: World Bank staff estimates based on sources and methods described in the World Bank's The Changing Wealth of Nations.

NY.GDP.NGAS.RT.ZS-gg.def: Natural gas rents are the difference between the value of natural gas production at regional prices and total costs of production.
NY.GDP.NGAS.RT.ZS-gg.name: Natural gas rents
NY.GDP.NGAS.RT.ZS-gg.source: World Bank staff estimates based on sources and methods described in the World Bank's The Changing Wealth of Nations.

NY.GDP.PETR.RT.ZS-gg.def: Oil rents are the difference between the value of crude oil production at regional prices and total costs of production.
NY.GDP.PETR.RT.ZS-gg.name: Oil rents
NY.GDP.PETR.RT.ZS-gg.source: World Bank staff estimates based on sources and methods described in the World Bank's The Changing Wealth of Nations.

NY.GDP.TOTL.RT.ZS-gg.def: Total natural resources rents are the sum of oil rents, natural gas rents, coal rents (hard and soft), mineral rents, and forest rents.
NY.GDP.TOTL.RT.ZS-gg.name: Total natural resources rents
NY.GDP.TOTL.RT.ZS-gg.source: World Bank staff estimates based on sources and methods described in the World Bank's The Changing Wealth of Nations.
